#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Sukhindriyavagga"
msgstr "4. The Pleasure Faculty"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Paṭhamasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta"
msgstr "34. Ascetics and Brahmins (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.34:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.34:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.34:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sukhindriyaṃ, dukkhindriyaṃ, somanassindriyaṃ, domanassindriyaṃ, "
"upekkhindriyaṃ."
msgstr "The faculties of pleasure, pain, happiness, sadness, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn48.34:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ "
"samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"nappajānanti, "
msgstr ""
"There are ascetics and brahmins who don’t truly understand the origin, "
"ending, gratification, drawback, and escape when it comes to these five "
"faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.34:1.5"
msgid ""
"na me te, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu vā samaṇasammatā "
"brāhmaṇesu vā brāhmaṇasammatā, na ca panete āyasmanto sāmaññatthaṃ vā "
"brahmaññatthaṃ vā diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"viharanti."
msgstr ""
"I don’t regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables don’t "
"realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and don’t live having "
"realized it with their own insight."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.34:2.1"
msgid ""
"Ye ca kho keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ "
"samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānanti, "
msgstr ""
"There are ascetics and brahmins who do truly understand the origin, ending, "
"gratification, drawback, and escape when it comes to these five faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.34:2.2"
msgid ""
"te kho me, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu ceva samaṇasammatā "
"brāhmaṇesu ca brāhmaṇasammatā, te ca panāyasmanto sāmaññatthañca "
"brahmaññatthañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"viharantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"I regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables realize the "
"goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and live having realized it with "
"their own insight.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.34:2.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
